<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-04-29T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-04-29T00:00:00-05:00" n="649" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d649">
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Memorandum from French embassy.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <p>Could the Department of State inform the French ambassador whether the
                            Spanish schooner <hi rend="italic">Sofia</hi> is among the number of
                            vessels captured by the Federal fleet?</p>
                        <closer><dateline rendition="#left"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-04-29"><hi rend="italic">April 29,
                                1898</hi></date>.</dateline></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>